    <title>xv6环境准备</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/01/04/xv6_begin/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/01/04/xv6_begin/</id>
    <published>2020-01-04T13:19:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-01-04T13:39:14.912Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://github.com/mit-pdos/xv6-riscv" target="_blank" rel="noopener">xv6</a>是mit的教学操作系统, 使用riscv指令集. 如下记录在Ubuntu 18.04上的实验环境准备:</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>详细内容可参考<a href="https://pdos.csail.mit.edu/6.828/2019/tools.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mit 6.828</a>.</p>
<p>第一步, 下载RISC-V的GNU工具链.<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git clone --recursive https://github.com/riscv/riscv-gnu-toolchain </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>第二步, 安装一些依赖环境.<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt install autoconf automake autotools-dev curl libmpc-dev libmpfr-dev libgmp-dev gawk build-essential bison flex texinfo gperf libtool patchutils bc zlib1g-dev libexpat-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>第三步, 编译安装RISC-V工具链.<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo mkdir /opt/qemu</span><br><span class="line">$ cd riscv-gnu-toolchain</span><br><span class="line">$ ./config --prefix=/opt/qemu</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo make -j$(nproc)</span><br><span class="line">$ cd ..</span><br><span class="line">$ export PATH=/opt/qemu/bin:$&#123;PATH&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>第四步, 安装QEMU 4.2.<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ wget https://download.qemu.org/qemu-4.2.0.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line">$ tar -xvf qemu-4.2.0.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line">$ cd qemu-4.2.0</span><br><span class="line">$ ./configure --disable-kvm --disable-werror --prefix=/opt/qemu --target-list=&quot;riscv64-softmmu&quot;</span><br><span class="line">$ make -j$(nproc)</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo make install</span><br><span class="line">$ cd ..</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>第五步, 测试.<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ riscv64-unknown-elf-gcc --version</span><br><span class="line">riscv64-unknown-elf-gcc (GCC) 9.2.0</span><br><span class="line">$ qemu-system-riscv64 --version</span><br><span class="line">QEMU emulator version 4.2.0</span><br><span class="line">$ git clone https://github.com/mit-pdos/xv6-riscv.git</span><br><span class="line">$ cd xv6-riscv</span><br><span class="line">$ make qemu</span><br><span class="line"># ... lots of outpu ...</span><br><span class="line">init: starting sh</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><code>Ctrl-A X</code>可退出QEMU.</p>
]]></content>
    
